==================================================
                 .:[NCPRJ v0.1]:.
==================================================
confproj  - Project for generating makefiles for a
            project.

NOTE: Run this command inside of a C source
directory.
--------------------------------------------------
creatproj - Main project use this to create an
            entire project.

NOTE: First use 1, to create a new directory.
Second, use 3 to add files to new directory. Next,
use 4 to generate a makefile for the new project.

NOTE: Option 2, to change to a different directory
instead of using the current directory.
==================================================
                    .:[EOF]:.
==================================================
